                        <interp inst="t18400302-name-856" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS WILSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a public-house in St. John-street, Clerkenwell—these pots are mine—I had seen the prisoner in and out of my house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I have been out of work ever since Christmas—my wife and two children had nothing to eat—I meant to sell the pots to get a loaf of bread—the officer will state how he found my place.</p>
